    // posthumous divinization in cult from the Ur III period onward
    // (Sin-Kashid of Uruk built the É-KI.KAL temple to Lugalbanda and
    // Ninsun together). At his union with Ninsun he was mortal-tier;
    // the deification is later overlay.

