    //  Part I (BAE 21st Annual Report, 1903) and Part II (BAE 43rd
    //  Annual Report, 1928). Modern: Daniel Richter, The Ordeal of the
    //  Longhouse (1992); William Fenton, The Great Law and the Longhouse
    //  (1998); Barbara Mann, Iroquoian Women: The Gantowisas (2000);
    //  Mann & Fields, "A Sign in the Sky: Dating the League of the
    //  Haudenosaunee" (American Indian Culture and Research Journal 21
    //  no. 2, 1997). Community-led: Onondaga Nation Council of Chiefs
