    // ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    // PHASE 3 — Hindu 3rd-generation scions: Janamejaya line + Añjanaparvan
    // The Janamejaya frame-narrative is the structural-narrative-frame of
    // the Mahābhārata itself (the epic is told by Vaiśampāyana at his
    // sarpasattra). Śatānīka the son of Janamejaya continues the line into
    // the Kuru-tier post-scion future per the Viṣṇu Purāṇa genealogy.
