      name: { primary: 'Iulia Caesaris', alt: ['Iulia (Caesar\'s daughter)', 'Iulia Pompei (after marriage)'], transliterations: { latin: 'Iulia Caesaris', etymology: 'Latin: Iulia — the canonical female-form of the gens-name Iulius. By Roman naming convention, all daughters of the gens Iulia were named Iulia; the cognomen Caesaris ("of Caesar") distinguishes the Dictator\'s daughter from the multiple other contemporary Iuliae.' } },
