  // 1194-1184 BCE, Aeneas's arrival in Italy ~1183 BCE, the Alban Kings
  // sequence covering the ~400-year gap to Romulus's traditional 753 BCE
  // foundation. Roman-internal eras follow the canonical Beard/North/Price
  // periodization. Variant names (roman-republic-late, roman-empire-julio-
